title: Categorized Grouping Transaction Behavior and Input/Output Data - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: Transaction Behavior Emits The agents does not emit any commands. Retrieves Command Description Command Description Cancel Batch If a cancelBatch is emitted by any agent in the workflow, all data in the current transaction will be disregarded. No closing conditions will be applied. Input/Output Data The agent receives UDRs of CGAgentInUDR type and emits UDRs of CGAgentOutUDR type.
